Police are increasing patrols in this area. Anyone with information is asked to contact the Old Dominion University Police by phone at 757-683-4000, or via text at the ODU LiveSafe App. 
Members of the community are asked to remain vigilant, be aware of their surroundings and avoid walking alone, and report any suspicious activity to the police by phone or via the LiveSafe App, available as a free download.